==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: anuran
<hw>anuran</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>an amphibian of the order
<ord>Anura</ord>; any of various tailless stout-bodied amphibians with
long hind limbs for leaping; semiaquatic and terrestrial species; a frog
or toad.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> frog, toad, toadfrog, batrachian,
salientian</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>anuran</ent>⟦br⟧

